name: The Sun
description:
* When I awoke the suns pattern was bright on me. I felt it's gentle heat and heard the noise of cicadas sizzle from the earth. 

Created with canvas. Each output uses a random hash to generate. Easily saved as an svg for plotting.

Click anywhere on the page to reload the output.

Press:
- 'c' to colorize
- 'i' to invert the background and stroke color
- 'p' to save the output as an svg (always saves as white background)
- 's' key to show seed.
